OL,3,COver half of young people unsure where
OL,4,Cto turn for mental health support
OL,6,FA new report has revealed over half of
OL,7,Fyoung people do not know where to turn
OL,8,Ffor mental health support.
OL,10,FThe joint report, published today by
OL,11,FHealthcare Inspectorate Wales (HIW),
OL,12,FCare Inspectorate Wales (CIW), and
OL,13,FEstyn revealed that many children and
OL,14,Fyoung people are still struggling to
OL,15,Faccess the help they need, when they
OL,16,Fneed it.
OL,18,FThe findings highlight the need for
OL,19,Fimprovements in mental health support
OL,20,Ffor children and young people.
