OL,3,COver half of young people unsure where
OL,4,Cto turn for mental health support
OL,6,FThe report included data from 215
OL,7,Fchildren and young people, 200 parents
OL,8,Fand carers, as well as 252
OL,9,Fprofessionals. It revealed over half
OL,10,Fof children and young people aged 11
OL,11,Fto 16 did not know where to turn for
OL,12,Fsupport. It also showed that when help
OL,13,Fwas needed, it was not always
OL,14,Favailable.
OL,16,FConcerns were also raised about
OL,17,Ffunding, poor communication between
OL,18,Fservices, and a lack of coordinated
OL,19,Fcare, leading to calls for stronger
OL,20,Fpartnerships between health and local
OL,21,Fauthorities.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/11
