OL,3,COver half of young people unsure where
OL,4,Cto turn for mental health support
OL,6,FDisparities were highlighted with
OL,7,Fregards to the eligibility criteria
OL,8,Fand thresholds for accessing CAMHS,
OL,9,Fleaving many families and
OL,10,Fprofessionals frustrated by the
OL,11,Fcommunication and lack of clarity
OL,12,Faround how decisions are made.
OL,14,FIt was also noted that those who speak
OL,15,FWelsh were not easily able to converse
OL,16,Fin their language of choice for mental
OL,17,Fhealth care and support.
