OL,3,COver half of young people unsure where
OL,4,Cto turn for mental health support
OL,6,FDespite shorter waiting times for
OL,7,Finitial CAMHS assessments, follow-up
OL,8,Fcare remained a major challenge for
OL,9,Fall children and young people. This
OL,10,Fappeared to be the case particularly
OL,11,Ffor those with complex needs,
OL,12,Fincluding care experienced and
OL,13,Fneurodiverse young people.
