OL,3,COver half of young people unsure where
OL,4,Cto turn for mental health support
OL,6,FThe report also stated that new
OL,7,Finitiatives like Sanctuary Spaces and
OL,8,FCrisis Hubs were providing
OL,9,Falternatives to emergency room care
OL,10,Ffor children and young people in
OL,11,Fcrisis. However, due to high demand,
OL,12,Fmany were only accessing support when
OL,13,Fthey reached breaking point.
