OL,3,COver half of young people unsure where
OL,4,Cto turn for mental health support
OL,6,FAlun Jones, Chief Executive of
OL,7,FHealthcare Inspectorate Wales, said:
OL,8,F"This report highlights the urgent
OL,9,Fneed for improvement in mental health
OL,10,Fservices for our children and young
OL,11,Fpeople. While we commend the
OL,12,Fdedication of professionals who are
OL,13,Fworking tirelessly to provide support,
OL,14,Fmany children and young people are
OL,15,Fstill struggling to access the care
OL,16,Fthey need. We cannot allow a sense of
OL,17,Fhelplessness amongst children and
OL,18,Fyoung people to persist; every child
OL,19,Fin Wales should know where to turn for
OL,20,Fhelp and receive timely support,
OL,21,Fregardless of their location.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/11
