OL,3,COver half of young people unsure where
OL,4,Cto turn for mental health support
OL,6,F"The findings highlight both the
OL,7,Fprogress made and the significant gaps
OL,8,Fthat remain. We must improve
OL,9,Fcollaboration among health boards and
OL,10,Flocal authorities to create a more
OL,11,Fcoordinated system. This is not just
OL,12,Fabout improving services; it's about
OL,13,Fensuring that every child and young
OL,14,Fperson in Wales has the right mental
OL,15,Fhealth support they need."
