OL,6,FChief Inspector of Care Inspectorate
OL,7,FWales, Gillian Baranski added: "Mental
OL,8,Fhealth support for our children and
OL,9,Fyoung people is not just a statistic;
OL,10,Fit's a call to action. It's deeply
OL,11,Fconcerning that over half of Wales's
OL,12,Fchildren and young people don't know
OL,13,Fwhere to turn for help."
