OL,3,COver half of young people unsure where
OL,4,Cto turn for mental health support
OL,6,FShe continued: "We recognise the
OL,7,Fimmense strain this places on
OL,8,Findividuals, families, and our
OL,9,Fdedicated professionals in health,
OL,10,Feducation, and local authorities.
OL,11,FWhile initiatives like Crisis Hubs
OL,12,Foffer hope, we must do more. We are
OL,13,Fcommitted to fostering better
OL,14,Fcollaboration between services,
OL,15,Faddressing gaps in care, and working
OL,16,Ftirelessly towards a mental health
OL,17,Fsupport system that is transparent,
OL,18,Faccessible, and effective for every
OL,19,Fchild and young person in Wales."
