OL,6,FA Welsh Government spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"We thank HIW, CIW and Estyn for this
OL,8,Fjoint review. It shows the progress
OL,9,Fmade to reduce waiting times and
OL,10,Fpositive developments in schools to
OL,11,Fsupport young people, and single
OL,12,Fpoints of access for CAMHS. However,
OL,13,Fthere are clearly areas where further
OL,14,Fand ongoing improvement is needed.
OL,16,F"We are committed to ensuring children
OL,17,Fand young people can get the support
OL,18,Fthey need, when they need and believe
OL,19,Fthere should be no wrong door for
OL,20,Fmental health support.
